<li><strong>Topical antibiotics:</strong> <a href="https:///generics/clindamycin-209621?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Acne_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_4">Clindamycin</a> &amp;&nbsp;<a href="https:///generics/azithromycin-209411?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Acne_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_5">Azithromycin</a></li>
