<p dir="ltr">A sitz bath or hip bath is nothing but a warm water bath that can promote the healing of an anal fissure. You can take a sitz bath with warm water for at least 20 minutes twice daily. The bath should only cover the hips and can be taken with the help of a kit or in the bathtub.</p>
