<p dir="ltr"><strong>3. <a href="https:///ayurveda/coconut-88?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Anal fissure_home_care_9_cta_link_2">Coconut</a> (Nariyal):</strong> Coconut oil has excellent healing properties and also works as a natural lubricating agent. Applying coconut oil around the anal region twice a day helps in dealing with anal fissures.</p>
